Fix #27: possible buffer overrun in uev_run()

If uev_init1() is called with maxevents > 10 the call to epoll_wait()
might cause buffer overflow.  Reported by Steve Palmer.

Bump ABI version 2.3.0 -> 3.0.0

The change in the uev_t means the stack space required, and used by
libuEv, is incompatible with previous releases.  So applications
need to be rebuild against the new header file.
